{"tid":563636,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 10 將加入極致效能「Ultimate Performance」模式","createTime":"2018-02-17T06:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T06:48:28.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aeb0d74b319a06b49c0817bf2585a115ed349c3e","tid":563636,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"美國時間 2 月 14 日微軟推出「Windows 10 Insider Preview」預覽版的最新版本「Build 17101」，當中作為 Windows 10 Pro for Workstations 的新功能之一，在電源選項當中，加入了一項極致效能「Ultimate Performance」模式。有消息指在 3 月至 4 月加入的更新當中（代號：Redstone 4 或稱 2 RS4）用戶會使用到這項新功能。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/xbox-one-windows-10-670x335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.makeuseof.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2Fxbox-one-windows-10-670x335.jpg&h=2a303320&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/16/windows-10-ultimate-performance/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2Fwindows-10-ultimate-performance%2Fnotebook%2F&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6AgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=40212ade\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/16/windows-10-ultimate-performance/notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"720c123f55a0a6cfe038c1691e18d1a54245c845","tid":563636,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:43:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/144116_a19df2f40c3b5c8c5e3cd1d039dcd27f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F17%2F144116_a19df2f40c3b5c8c5e3cd1d039dcd27f.gif&h=b7be2bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在 Windows 的電源選項當中，有考慮到電池消耗、節能與電腦效能的不同模式。而使用了這個極致效能模式後，會除去所有因節能而對硬件的所有限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但就會比一般的情況更加消耗電力。相信此模式是給一些工作站電腦，以及高配置電腦的用戶使用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n消息指這項極致效能「Ultimate Performance」模式只能在 Windows 10 Pro 上提供。手提電腦沒有插上電源時亦不能使用。</div>"},{"pid":"6b44c80d08d12ba9b9128ed83d541e80e58b1309","tid":563636,"uid":96741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aeb0d74b319a06b49c0817bf2585a115ed349c3e","tid":563636,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"美國時間 2 月 14 日微軟推出「Windows 10 Insider Preview」預覽版的最新版本「Build 17101」，當中作為 Windows 10 Pro for Workstations 的新功能之一，在電源選項當中，加入了一項極致效能「Ultimate Performance」模式。有消息指在 3 月至 4 月加入的更新當中（代號：Redstone 4 或稱 2 RS4）用戶會使用到這項新功能。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.makeuseof.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/xbox-one-windows-10-670x335.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.makeuseof.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F09%2Fxbox-one-windows-10-670x335.jpg&h=2a303320&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/02/16/windows-10-ultimate-performance/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2Fwindows-10-ultimate-performance%2Fnotebook%2F&d=825nkqZtgwYwYKRIcmS6AgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=40212ade\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/02/16/windows-10-ultimate-performance/notebook/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T06:48:28.000Z","msg":"雷神升壓渦"}]}